<p style="MARGIN: 6pt 0in"><a name="INSERT_SCHEDULE"></a><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">The Billings Area - Crow Service Unit, Indian Health Service (IHS) is requesting quotes in response to RFQ-CSU-19-028-RDJ for the Mobile Mammography services for the Crow Service Unit, Crow/Northern Cheyenne Hospital, Lodge Grass Health Center, and Pryor Health Center.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>The CSU/IHS will be awarding a fixed price contract to the successful offeror for the services as provided in the scope of work. </span></p>
<p style="MARGIN: 6pt 0in; LINE-HEIGHT: normal"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">This procurement is being conducted under Simplified Acquisition procedures pursuant to the authority of FAR 13.5, Simplified Procedures for Certain Commercial Items; FAR 37.4 - Nonpersonal Health Care Services, in which the contractor is an independent contractor; </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">Part 12.603, Streamlined Solicitation for Commercial Items.<br /></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">The purpose of this acquisition is </span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">to provide Mobile Mammography examinations for the patients of the Crow Service Unit.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span>The technologist will complete examinations and procedures, which are used in medical diagnosis utilizing stationary/mobile equipment assigned in the Crow/Northern Cheyenne Hospital Radiology Department</span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: ">. </span></p>
